    </div>

    <p>The gummy format has made B12 supplementation more accessible, particularly for older adults who may have difficulty swallowing capsules and for younger consumers who prefer a pleasant daily routine. The critical distinction between B12 gummies lies in the form of cobalamin used — methylcobalamin versus cyanocobalamin — which directly impacts how efficiently your body can utilize the vitamin.</p>

