      </div>
      <div class="info-card">
        <div class="info-card-ico"><Icon name="flask" size={22} /></div>
        <h3>Cyanocobalamin</h3>
        <p>Synthetic form with excellent shelf stability. Must be converted in the body through a two-step process. More affordable and well-studied. Effective for raising serum B12 levels in most individuals.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="info-card">
        <div class="info-card-ico"><Icon name="brain" size={22} /></div>
        <h3>Neurological Function</h3>
        <p>B12 is essential for myelin synthesis — the protective sheath around nerve fibers. Deficiency causes irreversible nerve damage if untreated, manifesting as numbness, tingling, and balance problems.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="info-card">
        <div class="info-card-ico"><Icon name="heart" size={22} /></div>
        <h3>Cardiovascular Health</h3>
        <p>B12 converts homocysteine to methionine. Elevated homocysteine is an independent risk factor for cardiovascular disease. Adequate B12 helps maintain healthy homocysteine levels alongside folate.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

