        <li><strong>Conducted taste and texture evaluation.</strong> Four editorial team members evaluated each gummy on flavor, sweetness, texture, and aftertaste over a two-week period. Scores were averaged and factored into the ranking.</li>
        <li><strong>Calculated long-term value.</strong> Cost per serving was computed using retail price divided by servings per container. We also calculated cost per 1000mcg of B12 to normalize value comparison across different dosage levels.</li>
